AUTOO PRIVACY POLICY

Last Updated: December 27, 2024

1. INFORMATION WE COLLECT

Autoo collects the following information:
- Car information you provide (make, model, year, mileage)
- Audio recordings you create for diagnostic purposes
- Device information for app functionality

2. HOW WE USE YOUR INFORMATION

We use your information to:
- Provide car sound diagnosis services
- Improve our AI analysis accuracy
- Send maintenance reminders (if enabled)

3. DATA STORAGE

- All car and diagnostic data is stored locally on your device
- Audio recordings are processed for analysis and not stored on external servers
- Subscription data is managed by RevenueCat and Apple

4. THIRD-PARTY SERVICES

We use the following services:
- OpenAI for AI-powered sound analysis
- RevenueCat for subscription management
- Apple for in-app purchases and payments

5. DATA SHARING

We do not sell or share your personal data with third parties for marketing purposes.

6. YOUR RIGHTS

You can:
- Delete all app data by uninstalling the app
- Reset app data within the app settings
- Contact us to request data deletion

7. CHILDREN'S PRIVACY

Autoo is not intended for children under 13 years of age.

8. CHANGES TO THIS POLICY

We may update this policy periodically. Continued use of the app constitutes acceptance of any changes.

9. CONTACT US

For privacy inquiries, contact us at:
Email: mytychdominik@gmail.com
